{"tid":145950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[哲學JJ]深夜想暢談人生，秒回#yup#","createTime":"2017-03-06T15:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T23:39:15.000Z","uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f36acdaccbdcde212b62699b4d252f9c3a24c33d","tid":145950,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:55:06.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲會咁諗吓我地嘅人生到底有咩意義<br />\n當我地每日淨大眼，發覺你所擁有嘅野隨時失去，發覺世界同你所預期之中完全唔符合，或者我地活著其實就只係純生存，冇咩意義，番工收工番工收工，日日如是，咁其實我地到最後得到啲咩<br />\n最後只會係得到嘅會係無窮無盡嘅空虛寂寞感。<br />\n<br />\n有時侯可能我會對人生充滿憧憬，果一刻真係會好努力裝備自己，但無奈重重波折，好似個天想玩你咁，不斷嘅失敗，不斷嘅努力白費，到最後其實我地做出嚟嘅野，叫做成長。<br />\n<br />\n人生難免陷入低谷，但係我地應該係要積極咁面對，抑或係消極面對呢。<br />\n<br />\n就好似我咁，其實中學頭果4年來都係白白咁浪費，因為鐘意打機，搞到日打夜打，難以抽身，到最後，我用咗3，4個月慢慢咁戒，先可以領悟到打機其實要適可而止，過份咁投入落去最後只會令我前途盡毀。 <br />\n到咗中五，我先至發覺時日無多，原來咁快就要考埋啲咩公開試，果陣時嘅我對呢樣野毫無觸覺，覺得可以再 hea過，溫咩撚嘢書吖。但係最後比我嘅啟蒙老師屌醒咗，<br />\n<br />\n「如果你想做廢柴我唔阻你，但係我覺得你放盡全力唔會係一條廢柴，套用每個人身上都係。」<br />\n<br />\n呢句對我嘅後期影響好深，中五後期都算盡力讀書中，勉勉強強叫做合格。中六之後，好比心機去溫習(利申冇底) ，直到考完個公開試，原來我都叫做勉強係中下層。<br />\n<br />\n到咗之後，我不斷咁係各方努力進步，心態本身係好懶散，唔認真，到最後而家好好咁裝備自己，力求上進，同埋會好好咁透徹思考(雖然有時都會fail)<br />\n呢個就係我暫時性人生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知巴絲你地而家個人生過成點，有冇咩迷惘地方，唔怕放低一齊傾一齊諗，冇人係完美，亦冇人係廢柴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60dbe181ef3a60bd5bb3eec3eabb3f95230691f6","tid":145950,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e072e224500104544c745dd76428c5d482a34a2","tid":145950,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"唔通話你聽你廢架啦讀唔到書咩<br />\n家長日d老師句句都係咁架啦<br />\n陳太，你個仔唔懶其實好聰明架⋯之類"},{"pid":"c1ab4c8545f3900f2e602ae86195b5d4c872ffa9","tid":145950,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔通話你聽你廢架啦讀唔到書咩<br />\n家長日d老師句句都係咁架啦<br />\n陳太，你個仔唔懶其實好聰明架⋯之類</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者可能係咁 先造就咗我地呢<br />\n有幾多老師(教畜)係會睇住你地死 大家都知"},{"pid":"d208ab1c1386c6c3f59ec2deaddaddc10d4662dc","tid":145950,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔通話你聽你廢架啦讀唔到書咩<br />\n家長日d老師句句都係咁架啦<br />\n陳太，你個仔唔懶其實好聰明架⋯之類</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者可能係咁 先造就咗我地呢<br />\n有幾多老師(教畜)係會睇住你地死 大家都知</blockquote><br />\n教畜<br />\n最憎<br />\n教ict既真係全部都係垃圾教畜黎"},{"pid":"36b3066a89d3e5ed3af66c3f7dedee3cede62b1f","tid":145950,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:02:38.000Z","msg":"放低傾吓 佢地做過啲咩仆街嘢嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ba6750197683258e3314b6612bb721f9284836","tid":145950,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放低傾吓 佢地做過啲咩仆街嘢嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d好好但又唔撚識教書 靠關係無料既教畜又有<br />\n個排真係好depressed"},{"pid":"7372fd840a1d11c29e0d6efbc7d16fc97ec30e97","tid":145950,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:06:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>放低傾吓 佢地做過啲咩仆街嘢嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d好好但又唔撚識教書 靠關係無料既教畜又有<br />\n個排真係好depressed</blockquote><br />\n唔緊要，都係朝住成長果方面進法啫，諗一諗每樣事都有佢正面之處，就當作磨練。<br />\n<br />\nBtw 冇巴絲肯吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9439987460338e4d2e496cda3b17170ed5caaa3c","tid":145950,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e33d61d780b36263ab46ae4fdf57f5ebd129bf6","tid":145950,"uid":5638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"人生存有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45549c9c1e9067ce50bde30eaad35ce6fb6b25ba","tid":145950,"uid":77707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:52:23.000Z","msg":"咁你而家有啲咩成就或做左啲乜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nor做緊乜"},{"pid":"6e34527bdfc5ca17389012cc474c5f9beb27b34b","tid":145950,"uid":69090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cca09f1ce7ada5b28a79523abd1628c964228ee7","tid":145950,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好努力讀書<br />\n係咪未夠努力所以冇人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有fd英文SBA俾人壟斷左講得一兩次嘢都高分過我<br />\n連miss都話我輸運氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢高分過你同你輸運氣係獨立事件"},{"pid":"6c6a8d63911aebb17d1581a21daa28fcaeeca99f","tid":145950,"uid":69090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:04:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"219f6ecf7e89f6f70c7cb7911dde74cec0ef0047","tid":145950,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:22:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人生存有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得生存嘅意義在於你會有件事係想認真去做，想呢世人唔後悔<br />\n<br />\n只要你認真去做一件事，佢必然有佢嘅意義嘅我諗"},{"pid":"f69f118192bef5096cc5e42908f2472ae0e056e0","tid":145950,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你而家有啲咩成就或做左啲乜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nor做緊乜</blockquote><br />\n用緊廢青 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e6b9f24ace920dee3b3c167b5f129fec48ea39","tid":145950,"uid":52918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好努力讀書<br />\n係咪未夠努力所以冇人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有fd英文SBA俾人壟斷左講得一兩次嘢都高分過我<br />\n連miss都話我輸運氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好氣餒，出到嚟其實你會比佢識更多or做嘅嘢會比佢更有效率"}]}